   {:e #blake3 "764a7eace95f3ddeaf88021ebb6bc2a9404598c562c3fb2d227ee87c28f0ebd4" :a :task/description :v "CONTEXT: Tests for online calibration + E2E verification.\n\nUNIT TESTS (3 in observe.rs or concept.rs tests):\n\n1. test_online_calibration_convergence:\n   - Fresh store with innate concepts. Make 5 observations via observe command.\n   - After observation 3: verify :config/concept.join-threshold datom exists.\n   - After observation 5: verify threshold differs from bootstrap default (0.20 for model2vec, 0.65 for hash).\n   - After observation 5: verify :config/calibration.similarity-count == '5'.\n\n2. test_online_calibration_statistics_correct:\n   - Known similarities [0.3, 0.5, 0.7]. Mean=0.5, variance=0.0267, stddev=0.163.\n   - Threshold = 0.5 - 0.5*0.163 = 0.418. Temperature = 0.163/2 = 0.082.\n   - Verify the formula produces these values.\n\n3. test_online_calibration_clamp:\n   - If all similarities are very high (e.g., 0.95, 0.96, 0.97), threshold should be clamped to <= 0.85.\n   - If all similarities are very low (e.g., 0.05, 0.06, 0.07), threshold should be clamped to >= 0.15.\n\nE2E VERIFICATION (extend existing e2e_calibrating_threshold.sh):\n- Add check: after observation 3, query :config/concept.join-threshold — should exist.\n- Add check: after observation 5, compare threshold to bootstrap default — should differ.\n- Add check: concept member counts should NOT all be identical after 8 observations (discrimination test).\n\nDEPENDS-ON: ONLINE-1." :op :assert}
